<div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>


        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <%= image_tag "profile.jpg"  , width: 290, alt: "profile image"%>
                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do |skill|%>
                        <h4><%= skill.title%></h4>
                        <div class="progress">
                            <div class="progess-bar progess-bar-striped bg-warning"
                                 role="progressbar"
                                 aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized%>"
                                 aria-valuemax="100"
                                 style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized%>%">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    <%end%>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>Ruby on Rails, ReactJS & Bootstrap are my main fields of knowledge. Also an SEO hobbyist who prefers VIM over anything else.
                Prefer clean code over more functionalities , ALWAYS. It is the responsibility of the developer to protect the code.</p>
                <p>BTech student at Jaypee University Of Information Technology, Waknaghat. From Kullu, Himachal Pradesh, India.</p>


                <button
                 class="btn btn-primary"
                 type="button"
                 data-toggle="collapse"
                 data-target="#jobHistory"
                 aria-expanded="false"
                 aria-controls="jobHistory"

                 >
                 Job History
                </button>

                    <button
                 class="btn btn-primary"
                 type="button"
                 data-toggle="collapse"
                 data-target="#education"
                 aria-expanded="false"
                 aria-controls="education"

                 >
                 Education
                    </button>

                        <p>
                        <div class=" collapse" id="jobHistory">
                            <div class="card card-block">
                                Only Freelance Projects so far.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </p>

                        <p>
                        <div class=" collapse" id="education">
                            <div class="card card-block">
                                LKG - XII : La Montessori School , Kullu
                            </div>
                            <div class="card card-block">
                                XI-XII : Ambition Classes, Kullu
                            </div>
                            <div class="card card-block">
                                B.Tech (Computer Science): Jaypee University Of Information Technology, Waknaghat, Solan
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
